---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: "Our Services"
seoTitle: "Post-Frame Building Services in Michigan"
description: "Pole barns, garages, horse barns, and barndominiums built across southeast Michigan. See every post-frame service and get a free estimate."
permalink: /services/
---

{# ========== SERVICES INDEX ========== #}

<header class="ohero noimg slim">
  <div class="wrap"><div class="ohero-inner stagger">
    <span class="lab">What we build</span>
    <h1>Our Services</h1>
    <p class="lead">Pole barns, garages, horse barns, barndominiums, and steel buildings. Pick a service below to see project photos and details, or call us if you are not sure what you need.</p>
    <div class="hero-cta">
      <a href="/contact/" class="btn btn-green">Get a Free Estimate</a>
    </div>
  </div></div>
</header>

<section class="blk"><div class="wrap">
  <div class="head reveal"><h2>Everything we build</h2><p>Eleven post-frame services, from full builds to repairs and tear-downs.</p></div>
  <div class="svc stagger">
    {% for service in collections.services %}
    <a class="card" href="{{ service.url }}">
      <div class="im"><img src="{{ service.data.image }}" alt="{{ service.data.subtitle or service.data.title }}" loading="lazy"></div>
      <div class="bd">
        <h3>{{ service.data.title }}</h3>
        <p>{{ service.data.subtitle }}</p>
        <span class="lk">Learn more &rarr;</span>
      </div>
    </a>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
  <div class="more-link reveal" style="margin-top:34px"><a href="/steel-buildings/">Need pre-engineered steel instead? See the steel building line &rarr;</a></div>
</div></section>

<section class="blk cta"><div class="wrap"><div class="box reveal">
  <h2>Not sure what you need?</h2>
  <p>Tell us about your project and we will recommend the right building. Free estimates, no pressure.</p>
  <div class="row">
    <a href="/contact/" class="btn btn-gold">Get a Free Estimate</a>
    <span class="or">or call</span>
    <a class="bigph" href="tel:{{ site.phoneTel }}">{{ site.phone }}</a>
  </div>
</div></div></section>
